ygData.subject: Re: Where are Tinny daggers in Qeynos?
ygData.msgSnippet: Sorry but your going to have to hop back on the boat. Unless a new vender appeared in the last two months there are no tiny daggers for sale at a vendor unless
ygData.messageBody:
Sorry but your going to have to hop back on the boat.
Unless a new vender appeared in the last two months there are no tiny
daggers for sale at a vendor unless a player sold them to the vendor. Then
they would not be there long.
Stonedreamer
